  <bioghist id="aspace_89538f6482dff7144c650957b0059cb0">
    <head>ORGANIZATIONAL HISTORY</head>
<p>Pro-Fac was a major fruit and vegetable processing cooperative founded and headquartered in Western New York. It was formed in 1961 and disbanded in 2012.</p>  </bioghist>
  <scopecontent id="aspace_36b38022c8eeb208475c9b40908fc3b2">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Includes correspondence, reports, meeting minutes, publications, audiotapes, slides, videotapes and photographs, documenting the history of the cooperative.</p>  </scopecontent>
